page.title: 01A First Look at our District
page.content: Tadley is surrounded mainly by rural areas.Very little of the district is covered by residential development.The vicinity is mainly dominated by forestland. Your first impression of our area will depend on which way you enter.The north side of our environment is mostly residential.The southern part of our environment is mainly rural.The central section is deciduous woodland. It was once owned by royalty but,now it is a nature reserve. We have many agricultural sections in our district.Tadley is the centre of our residential development. The main road through our vicinity is the{A340.}Apart from this there are no other main roads but the vicinity is criss-crossed with minor roads.
